## 4. Data Model (6 Collection)

### 4.1 `users`

```js
{
  _id: ObjectId,
  firstName: { type: String, required: true, minlength: 2, maxlength: 50, trim: true },
  lastName: { type: String, required: true, minlength: 2, maxlength: 50, trim: true },
  email: {
    type: String,
    required: true,
    unique: true,
    lowercase: true,
    trim: true,
    match: /^[\w.+-]+@[\w-]+\.[\w.-]+$/
  },
  password: { type: String, required: true, minlength: 6 }, // bcrypt hash
  companyName: { type: String, required: true, minlength: 2, maxlength: 100, trim: true },
